Cell Siege: Privacy policy

Cell Siege is an android game developed by Finidi Schoonhoven and released on the Google Play store under the name Olivegarden Android app developed by Wrichik Basu.

I hereby state, to the best of my knowledge and belief, that I have not programmed this application to collect any personally identifiable information. The only data stored by this application is data related to app settings, such as if the app's music was muted, and can be simply erased by clearing the app's data or uninstalling it.

This application makes use of Unity Ads for advertisment implementation (https://docs.unity.com/ads/en-us/manual/UnityAdsHome). It contains in-app purchased to get rid of advertisements through the Google Play store.

If you find any security vulnerability that has been inadvertently caused by me, or have any question regarding how the app protectes your privacy, please send me an email and I will surely try to fix it/help you.

Yours sincerely,
Finidi Schoonhoven (Olivegarden).
olivegardenapps@gmail.com
